---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About Abby | Chaos With Clarity" description="9 years finance: EY to fractional CFO. Poet, founder, and soul worker.">

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <section style="padding:10rem 3rem 5rem;background:#e8dcc8;border-bottom:1px solid #cec5ad;">
    <div style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;">
      <p style="font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-weight:400;">The Person</p>
      <h1 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(3.5rem,8vw,7rem);font-weight:600;color:#1a1612;letter-spacing:-0.02em;line-height:0.9;">About Abby</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MAIN ABOUT GRID -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:5rem 3rem;">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;border:1px solid #cec5ad;" class="about-grid">

      <!-- Photo col -->
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;border-right:1px solid #cec5ad;">
        <div style="aspect-ratio:4/5;background:#e8dcc8;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;border-bottom:1px solid #cec5ad;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
          <div style="text-align:center;">
            <i class="ph ph-user-circle" style="font-size:5rem;color:#cec5ad;display:block;margin-bottom:0.75rem;"></i>
            <p style="color:#b8ae9a;font-size:0.72rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;">Your photo here</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="padding:2.5rem 3rem;">
          <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;color:#7a7260;font-size:1.3rem;line-height:1.8;">
            "Spreadsheets couldn't answer the chest ache. So I write."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text col -->
      <div style="padding:3rem 3.5rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;gap:1.25rem;">
        <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.5rem;color:#1a1612;font-weight:500;line-height:1.4;letter-spacing:0.01em;">
          9 years in finance: EY to fractional CFO for founders.
        </p>
        <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.92rem;line-height:2;">Spreadsheets couldn't answer the chest ache.</p>
        <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.92rem;line-height:2;">So I write: money as fuel, death as teacher, freedom as breath.</p>
        <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.92rem;line-height:2;"><strong style="color:#1a1612;font-weight:500;">Chaos With Clarity</strong> = numbers + soul + raw.</p>
        <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.92rem;line-height:2;">Not therapy. Not coaching. A mirror. A pause.</p>
        <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.92rem;line-height:2;">If you're a founder caught between ambition and peace — if the numbers are good but something still feels wrong — let's talk.</p>

        <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;color:#c17f3a;font-size:1.2rem;margin-top:0.5rem;">– Abby</p>

        <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:0.75rem;margin-top:0.75rem;">
          <a href="/offerings" style="font-size:0.66rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;background:#c17f3a;color:#f3e8d8;padding:0.8rem 1.75rem;text-decoration:none;font-weight:400;">Work with Me</a>
          <a href="/writings" style="font-size:0.66rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;border:1px solid #cec5ad;color:#7a7260;padding:0.8rem 1.75rem;text-decoration:none;font-weight:400;">Read My Poems</a>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size:0.78rem;color:#b8ae9a;margin-top:0.5rem;">
          Looking for the CFO work?
          <a href="https://abbyjain.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:#c17f3a;text-decoration:none;margin-left:0.3rem;">abbyjain.com ↗</a>
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LONGER STORY -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:0 3rem 6rem;">
    <div style="max-width:46rem;margin:0 auto;">

      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1.25rem;margin-bottom:3rem;">
        <div style="width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#5d6b45;flex-shrink:0;"></div>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;color:#7a7260;font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:400;">The longer story</h2>
        <div style="flex:1;height:1px;background:#cec5ad;"></div>
      </div>

      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.5rem;">
        <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.93rem;line-height:2.1;">
          I started writing because the spreadsheets stopped making sense.
          Not financially — the numbers were always there. But existentially.
          You can model a company's runway to the day. You cannot model
          why you lie awake at 2am wondering if any of it means anything.
        </p>
        <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.93rem;line-height:2.1;">
          Nine years of finance — from audit rooms at EY to sitting across
          from founders who had everything and felt nothing — taught me one thing:
          clarity without depth is just noise with good formatting.
        </p>
        <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.93rem;line-height:2.1;">
          The poems started in a notebook. Then they started helping people.
          Not because they had answers, but because they named things that
          people had been carrying silently.
        </p>
        <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.93rem;line-height:2.1;">
          Chaos With Clarity is where I bring both sides together.
          The CFO who can read your runway and the poet who can sit with
          what the runway is actually for.
        </p>
        <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.93rem;line-height:2.1;">
          If that's the conversation you've been looking for — you're in the right place.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- JOIN STRIP -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:0 3rem 7rem;">
    <div style="border-top:1px solid #cec5ad;padding-top:3rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;" class="join-strip">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1.5rem;">
        <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;color:#7a7260;font-size:1.2rem;">Poems. Reflections. Circles. Inbox only.</p>
        <a href="/join" style="font-size:0.66rem;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;background:#c17f3a;color:#f3e8d8;padding:0.85rem 2rem;text-decoration:none;font-weight:400;white-space:nowrap;">Join the Chaos</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    .about-grid > div:first-child { border-right: none !important; border-bottom: 1px solid #cec5ad; }
  }
</style>
